                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "You capitalize on the fears your firearm engenders, terrifying your foes. Make a ranged Strike with this firearm against a target. If you successfully deal damage to your target, the target is also affected by a 4th-level  *phantasmal killer* with a spell DC of 28. While  *phantasmal killer* typically takes the shape of the target's worst fear, this effect always appears to the target in the form of a majestic and ferocious tiger.",
